    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "RPC is basically for dapps / used by dapp developers.  Every dapp developer I'm aware of currently uses geth.  If you change geth to make it conform to a different spec, this will almost certainly break currently functioning dapps.  My suggestion: **snapshot geth's current implementation and define that as the spec**, since it is already the de facto spec for everyone using the RPC system.\n",
